TITLE: Why userspace?

<ul>
<li>Ok, so I want a custom filesystem
<li>Why should I do it in userspace?

<BR><BR>

<li>Broken kernel code makes many people sad
<li>Kernel programming is harder than userspace programming
<li>There are lots of nice userspace libraries
<li>There are a <i>lot</i> of trained userspace coders out there
<li>Some things just don't make sense in kernel space
</ul>